                    <td>The forager spawns and wanders.. his wanderings can take him to that wall.  

As for Dronik, he's a wizard and he casts Ice Comet, Snare and other stuff.  Personally I just run up to wherever he is, mezz him, drain his mana then beat him down.  He hits harder than you might think and has a ton of mana though.  I've found my best bet was to melee him while dotting him as well.. throwning in a mezz here and there to interrupt casting... Psalm of Veeshan works well here as part of your twist if ...</td>
